{"tid":1579213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國司法部控斯諾登違保密協議 求充公出新書利益","createTime":"2019-09-18T13:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T13:31:29.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"418c3cb3b049d5977f5cec7d5a32919f1f09f201","tid":1579213,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:03:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190918/s00005/1568802952809/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%AF%E8%AB%BE%E7%99%BB%E9%81%95%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B1%82%E5%85%85%E5%85%AC%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%9B%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190918%2Fs00005%2F1568802952809%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2585%2585%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%259B%258A&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=c77559c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190918%2Fs00005%2F1568802952809%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%2581%2595%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2585%2585%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%259B%258A&h=2ecaf8e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190918/s00005/1568802952809/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%AF%E8%AB%BE%E7%99%BB%E9%81%95%E4%BF%9D%E5%AF%86%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B1%82%E5%85%85%E5%85%AC%E5%87%BA%E6%96%B0%E6%9B%B8%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019/9/18<br />\n<br />\n 共1幅 下一頁 <br />\n美國司法部周二（17日）起訴前中情局僱員斯諾登，指其新書《永久紀錄》（Permanent Record）出版前，書稿無提交予當局審查，稱有關內容與斯諾登的公開演說，均違反他與中情局和美國國家安全局的保密協議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司法部在聲明表示，是次訴訟並非要禁止新書發行，而是尋求充公斯諾登從新書獲得的所有收益。助理司法部長亨特（Jody Hunt）指出，「美國保護敏感國安資訊的能力，來自僱員與合約人員遵守保密協議」，強調司法部「不會容許個人違反出版前送審文稿的義務，以美國利益為代價獲利」。《永久紀錄》的出版商Macmillan Publishers同被列為被告，以「確保沒有資金會被轉移予斯諾登」。<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登的代表律師稱訴訟沒有理據（without merit），「新書內容並無包含過往從未被受尊重新聞機構發表過的政府機密」；又說若斯諾登認為政府會「真誠地」（in good faith）審查新書，早就會將書稿送審。<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登自2013年泄露包括「稜鏡計劃」（PRISM）在內的英美情報機構大型監控項目後，一度在香港匿藏，其後最終取道北京流亡到俄羅斯，在莫斯科定居至今。他在新書中透過，自己2013年被迫離開香港，是因為港府反對聯合國試圖給予他國際庇護。"},{"pid":"d1ac366f2755284bae57565c96ddf1bf2bb54066","tid":1579213,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5033d188982062bc509999ce37f94f79a3bfaf73","tid":1579213,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}